    "bio": "👋 Hi! I'm Arlin - a QA Engineer with 2 years of experience and a background in Dart & Flutter for mobile app development.\n⚙️ I'm passionate about automation and love building efficient workflows using n8n.\n📬 Reach out  for any help with custom workflows",
